title: Week 5 NFL Recap: SNF Recap, Eagles Undefeated, Giants stop Rodgers, Bills blow out Steelers, Cowboys rolling with Rush (Football 10/10)
description:
Will Brinson, Ryan Wilson, and John Breech recap an interesting Week 5 in the NFL. The Giants beat Rodgers in London, the Eagles barely stay undefeated, and the Cowboys roll over the Rams in LA.
